<p>40 = P</p>\n<p>Jika P = 40, maka</p>\n<p>Q = 2P &ndash; 50 = 2(40) &ndash; 50 = 80 &ndash; 50 = 30</p>\n<p>Maka, titik keseimbangan berada pada titik Q = 30 dan P = 40</p>',1),(1922,'<p>Semula harga barang Y pada tingkat harga Rp30.000,00/unit jumlah yang diminta 15 unit. Pada harga Rp40.000,00/unit jumlah yang diminta menjadi 10 unit. Maka, koefisien elastisitasnya ...</p>',1146,47,'inelastis','2020-12-16 05:10:27','2020-12-16 05:10:27',0,'<p>P1 = 30.000&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q1 = 15</p>\n<p>P2 = 50.000&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q2 = 10</p>\n<p>&Delta;P = 10.000&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &Delta;Q = 5</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img title=\"\\\\Ed \\ = \\frac{\\Delta Q}{\\Delta P} \\ X \\ \\frac{Q1}{P1} \\\\\\\\\\\\ Ed\\ = \\frac{5}{10.000} \\ X \\ \\frac{15}{30.000} \\\\\\\\\\\\ Ed \\ = \\frac{150.000}{300.000}\" src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?\\dpi{100}&amp;space;\\\\Ed&amp;space;\\&amp;space;=&amp;space;\\frac{\\Delta&amp;space;Q}{\\Delta&amp;space;P}&amp;space;\\&amp;space;X&amp;space;\\&amp;space;\\frac{Q1}{P1}&amp;space;\\\\\\\\\\\\&amp;space;Ed\\&amp;space;=&amp;space;\\frac{5}{10.000}&amp;space;\\&amp;space;X&amp;space;\\&amp;space;\\frac{15}{30.000}&amp;space;\\\\\\\\\\\\&amp;space;Ed&amp;space;\\&amp;space;=&amp;space;\\frac{150.000}{300.000}\" /></p>\n<p>Ed = 0,5</p>\n<p>Dari perhitungan tersebut d atas didapatkan koefisien elastisnya = 0,5, ketika Ed kurang dari 1 disebut Inelastis.</p>',1),(1923,'<p>Diketahui fungsi pendapatan Y =C+ S dan fungsi konsumsi C= 200+0,75Y. Jika tabungan sebesar Rp500,00. Maka, besar pendapatan adalah ...</p>',1146,47,'Rp2.800,00','2020-12-16 05:11:33','2020-12-16 05:11:33',0,'<p>Y = C + S</p>\n<p>Y = 200 + 0,75Y + 500</p>\n<p>Y = 700 + 0,75Y</p>\n<p>0,25 = 700</p>\n<p>Y = 2.800</p>',1),(1924,'<p>Di suatu bank tertulis:</p>\n<p>Kur