otel because it rained all day. They didn&rsquo;t predict the weather. Boring!</p>\n<p>Man : Let me guess. The hotel was terrible as well?</p>\n<p>Woman : You bet!</p>\n<p>What does the woman express?</p>',119,16,'Dissatisfaction','2020-12-23 18:41:18','2020-12-23 18:41:18',0,'<p>Si wanita pada dialog tidak menyukai liburannya karena dipenuhi hal-hal yang mengecewakan. Mulai dari kehilangan tas, sampai hotel yang tidak layak. Dengan begitu, jawaban yang tepat adalah B. &ldquo;<em>dissatisfaction</em>&rdquo;.</p>',1),(2803,'<p>A train accident occurred in northern Italy. The train traveled at 180 mph when the first car on the train left the rails and separated from the train. It hit a nearby railroad building, killed two railway workers, and injured 27 people.</p>\n<p>Police explained that there was some work on the railway the evening before; however, work on railways happens very often. Police have to investigate the accident because they do not know if the work caused the accident.</p>\n<p>Rail workers&rsquo; unions will go on strike on Friday. They said that the accident was very serious and not acceptable.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>What happened after the incident?</p>',119,16,'A protest would be held.','2020-12-23 18:42:40','2020-12-23 18:42:40',0,'<p>Setelah kecelakaan, serikat pekerja kereta api akan melakukan unjuk rasa karena mereka menilai bahwa kecelakaan tersebut sangat serius dan tidak dapat ditoleransi (<em>Rail workers&rsquo; unions will go on strike on Friday</em>). Jadi, jawaban yang tepat adalah B.&nbsp;<em>A protest would be held.</em></p>',1),(2804,'<p>Thomas Matulessy, also known as Kapitan Pattimura or Ahmad Lussy or simply Pattimura, was an Ambonese soldier and National Hero of Indonesia. Born on the island of Saparua, Pattimura joined the British army after they took the Maluku islands from the Dutch colonials. When the islands were returned to the Dutch in 1816, he was dismissed. Concerned that the Dutch would implement programs that limited his people, Pattimura led an armed rebellion that captured Fort Duurstede on 16 May 1817. Killing the inhabitants of the fortress and fighting off Dutch reinforcements, on 29 May he was declared the leader of the Maluku people. After being betrayed by the King of Booi Pati Akoon, he was captured by Dutch forces on 11 November and hanged the next month.</p>\n<p>Pattimura has become a symbol of both Maluku and Indonesian independence, praised by President Sukarno and declared a national hero by President Suharto. He has several namesakes both in the capital of Maluku, Ambon, and in the rest of the Indonesian archipelago.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>What can we infer from the monologue?</p>',119,16,'Pattimura was executed to stop the rebellion.','2020-12-23 18:44:10','2020-12-23 18:44:10',0,'<p>Kesimpulan yang tepat adalah C. Pattimura dihukum mati karena Belanda ingin agar para pemberontak kehilangan pemimpinnya dan pada akhirnya berhenti memberontak.</p>',1),(2805,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\">PUBLIC NOTICE</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This is to inform all members of Staff and the General Public that the Consulate General of the Federal Republic of Nigeria, Atlanta, will be closed on Monday November 11, 2019 to observe the Veteran\'s Day holiday declared by the United States Government.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Consulate General of Nigeria, Atlanta</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>What is the purpose of the text?</p>',119,16,'To announce the Consulate General of Nigeria closing due to the US Veteran’s Day.','2020-12-23 18:45:45','2020-12-23 18:45:45',0,'<p>Pengumuman di atas menginformasikan tentang penutupan Konsulat Jenderal Nigeria di Atlanta karena mereka akan merayakan Hari Veteran Amerika Serikat. Dengan begitu, jawaban yang tepat adalah B.</p>',1),(2806,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hello Felyta!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">It&rsquo;s been too long since our last visit, and I thought I&rsquo;d write to you to see how everything is. So, how are you and the family doing? I remember precisely and perfectly Janice is just about to start kindergarten, right? That must be exciting; she was always such a bright girl. And what grade is Silas going into? 7th or 8th? He&rsquo;s growing up so fast. They both are, really.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;My kids are getting ready for the school year as well. Galen just mentioned you guys the other day while we were at the park. He remembered how Janice was throwing the pebbles last time and asked when he&rsquo;d get to play with her again. I really hope that I can tell him you&rsquo;ll all be visiting soon. You guys should drive up for a weekend out with us. There&rsquo;s a new restaurant in town, and I think you&rsquo;d like it; it&rsquo;s very simple and cozy. &nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;We all miss you very much, Felyta, and the family is welcome to come visit any time at all. I hope all is well with everyone. Please send hellos from all of us to your family. Talk to you soon.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Love, Maria</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>From the text we know Maria remembered that ...</p>',119,16,'Felyta’s daughter was going to enter kindergarten.','2020-12-23 18:46:48','2020-12-23 18:46:48',0,'<p>Hal yang masih diingat Maria adalah Janice (anak Felyta) akan masuk TK tahun itu (<em>I remember precisely and perfectly Janice is just about to start kindergarten, right?</em>). Dengan begitu, jawaban yang tepat adalah C.</p>',1),(2807,'<p>The Great Wall of China is the largest and the longest wall to have ever built by humans. Several walls were being built from as early as the 7th century BC by ancient Chinese states; selective stretches were later joined together by Qin Shi Huang (220&ndash;206 BC), the first Emperor of China. Little of the Qin wall remains. Later on, many successive dynasties have built and maintained multiple stretches of border walls. The most well-known sections of the wall were built by the Ming dynasty (1368&ndash;1644)</p>\n<p>Collectively, the Great Wall stretches from Dandong in the east to Lop Lake in the west. The construction materials &nbsp;were mainly earth, wood, stones, sand, and bricks, used depending on construction era and construction site with different climate and local materials. Its average height ranges from 6 to 7 meters and the tallest part reaches around 14 meters. A comprehensive archaeological survey, using&nbsp;<strong><em>advanced</em></strong>&nbsp;technologies, has concluded that the walls built by the Ming dynasty measure 8,850 km. This is made up of 6,259 km sections of actual wall, 359 km of trenches and 2,232 km of natural defensive barriers such as hills and rivers. The entire wall with all of its branches measures out to be 21,196 km.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>using&nbsp;</em><strong><em><u>advanced </u></em></strong><em>technologies&rdquo;</em>&nbsp;(Par. 2). The underlined word is synonymous with &hellip;.</p>',119,16,'modern','2020-12-23 18:48:46','2020-12-23 18:48:46',0,'<p>Kata&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;advanced&rdquo;&nbsp;</em>artinya modern sehingga jawaban yang tepat adalah C. Kata&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;affordable&rdquo;</em>&nbsp;artinya terjangkau,&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;expensive&rdquo;&nbsp;</em>artinya mahal,&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;old&rdquo;</em>&nbsp;artinya tua, dan&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;useful&rdquo;</em>&nbsp;artinya berguna.</p>',1),(2808,'<p>Smoking a cigarette may be a normal routine to some, but in reality, it is purely a harmful activity. Ingesting smoke can be lethal, and can cause many diseases, such as cancer. But one common issue that most smokers overlook is its impact on others. This is known as secondhand smoke, the smoke produced from a cigarette or the smoke exhaled by a smoker. Secondhand smoke is a silent killer.</p>\n<p>Smoking doesn\'t only affect people, but also the environment. I am fairly certain that every person in this room has seen a cigarette butt lying somewhere, at some point in their lives. Whether it&rsquo;s on the curb of a neighborhood street, on the sandy beach, or in your favorite park, this litter can be found just about anywhere. Most smokers don&rsquo;t even believe that a cigarette butt is actually litter, but trust me, it is.</p>\n<p>I personally think that breathing clean and pure air is a basic right for any human being. Allowing public smoking is taking away that right, and making the air we breathe in daily possibly harmful to our well-being.</p>\n<p><em>\"Smoking doesn\'t only affect people, but also the environment.</em>&rdquo;</p>\n<p>Change the sentence above into passive voice!</p>',119,16,'People and environment are affected by smoking.','2020-12-23 18:49:43','2020-12-23 18:49:43',0,'<p>Kalimat pada soal ditulis menggunakan&nbsp;<em>simple present</em>&nbsp;(terdapat kata<em>&nbsp;&ldquo;doesn&rsquo;t&rdquo;</em>). Dengan begitu, kalimat pasifnya haruslah dalam bentuk&nbsp;<em>simple present</em>&nbsp;(<em>is/am/are + V3</em>). Jadi, jawaban yang tepat adalah A.</p>',1),(2809,'<p>Dear Mr. Ferguson,</p>\n<p>On the behalf of Domina Sales &amp; Marketing Pvt Ltd, I am glad to invite you for the business summit 2020 to be held at the head office of our company on Friday February, 21st, 2020. The subject of this business meet is the distribution of all saleable products. We have enclosed a business meet imitation containing all essential detail of summit including venue, meeting hours and subjects of discussions for your ready reference.</p>\n<p>We request you to bring all official documents in order to discuss all financial and distribution issues which you have been through in the year of 2019.</p>\n<p>Yours Sincerely,</p>\n<p>Manager- Sales &amp; Marketing</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Why is the text written?</p>',119,16,'To invite Mr. Ferguson to the business summit 2020.','2020-12-23 18:51:17','2020-12-23 18:51:17',0,'<p>Alasan si penulis mengirim surat kepada Mr. Ferguson dapat dilihat pada kalimat awal paragraf pertama:&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;</em><em><u>I am glad to invite you</u></em><em>&nbsp;for the business summit 2020&rdquo;.&nbsp;</em>Jadi, jawaban yang tepat adalah C.&nbsp;<em>To invite Mr. Ferguson to the business summit 2020.</em></p>',1),(2810,'<p>If they had informed us about the exam, we_____better score</p>',119,16,'Would have got','2020-12-23 19:01:42','2020-12-23 19:01:42',0,'<p>If clause diikuti pola had+V3 ( had informed), sehingga main clause dalam bentuk would have V3 (would have got)</p>',1),(2811,'<p>Unless they____us in doing the assignment, we wouldn&rsquo;t have finished the assignment on time.</p>',119,16,'Had helped','2020-12-23 19:02:29','2020-12-23 19:02:29',0,'<p>Unless adalah bentuk negatif dari if clause, sehingga harus diisi pola kalimat positif.<br />Di bagian main clause menggunakan pola would have V3 ( wouldn&rsquo;t have finished), sehingga setelah unless diikuti had V3 (had helped)</p>',1),(2812,'<p>Bats can find their preys in the darkness&hellip;their very keen eyesights</p>',119,16,'because of','2020-12-23 19:04:19','2020-12-23 19:04:19',0,'<p>&ldquo;Bats can find their preys in the darkness&rdquo; ..adalah sebuah clause/sentence yang menyatakan effect yang diikuti ..&ldquo;their very keen eyesights&rdquo;.. yang merupakan cause yang berupa Noun phrase, sehingga conjunction yang tepat adalah because of.</p>',1),(2813,'<p>The government has revised their policy on taxes and expenses____the economic condition is slowing down.</p>',119,16,'because','2020-12-23 19:04:52','2020-12-23 19:04:52',0,'<p>Pembahasan<br />The government has revised their policy on taxes and expenses&rdquo;.. adalah sebuah clause/sentence yang menyatakan effect yang diikuti..&rdquo;the economic condition is slowing down&rdquo;.. cause yang berupa clause/sentence, sehingga conjunction yang tepat adalah because .</p>',1),(2814,'<p>Andy bought not only a 