&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><sup>&nbsp;</sup>= log 2 +3 log 3</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;= a + 3b</p>',1),(2886,'<p>&nbsp;Persamaan grafik fungsi kuadrat di bawah ini adalah &hellip;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"http://103.41.207.247:3000/1608572085405-mtk akutan 4.jpg\" alt=\"1608572085405-mtk akutan 4.jpg\" width=\"208\" height=\"173\" /></p>',1150,51,'y = x2  + 2x +3','2020-12-21 17:36:42','2020-12-21 17:36:42',0,'<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>Grafik tersebut memotong sumbu X di titik (-3,0) dan (1,0) dan melalui titik (-1,-4)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Persamaan fungsi kuadrat apabila diketahui dua titik potong dengan sumbu X dan melalui sebuah&nbsp; titik :</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; y = a(x- x<sub>1</sub>)(x-x<sub>2</sub>)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; y = a(x + 3)(x-1) melalui titik (-1,-4):</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -4 = a(-1 + 3)(-1- 1)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -4 = a(2)(-2)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a = 1</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jadi, persamaan fungsi kuadrat:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; y = (x + 3) (x-1)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; =x<sup>2 </sup>+ 2x &ndash; 3</p>',1),(2887,'<table style=\"height: 264px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 73px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 73px; width: 629.258px;\" colspan=\"2\">\n<p>&nbsp;Jika x<sub>1</sub> dan x<sub>2</sub> adalah akar- akar persamaan kuadrat 2x<sup>2</sup> + 6x &ndash; 3 = 0 maka persamaan baru yang&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; akar-akarnya (x<sub>1 </sub>&ndash; 2)(x<sub>2</sub> &ndash; 2 ) adalah &hellip;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 52px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 52px; width: 313.008px;\">\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 52px; width: 313.008px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 52px;\">\n<td st